N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 333.1 - Application

State Regulations

The fee schedule applicable to psychological services shall
be the behavioral health fee schedule in effect on the date on which the
psychological services were rendered, regardless of the date of
accident. Notes
